==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Removed
<hw>Re*moved"</hw> <pr>(r?-m??vd")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Changed in place.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Dismissed from office.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Distant in location; remote.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Something
finer than you could purchase in so <xex>removed</xex> a
dwelling.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>Distant by degrees in relationship; <as>as, a cousin
once <ex>removed</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Re*mov"ed*ness</wf>
<pr>(r<?/-m<?/<?/v"<?/d-n<?/s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Remover</ent>⟦br⟧
